                "caption": "Figure 1:HUGlearns dexterous grasping without any robot data.Trained solely on egocentric human grasp data,HUGgenerates diverse human grasps for real-world objects in a single RGBD image captured from a stereo camera, which can be retargeted to robot hands for zero-shot, in-the-wild dexterous grasping.",
